file.name: ping-bearer-auth.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: ping test
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:8080/'
paths:
  /ping:
    get:
      operationId: pingGet
      responses:
        '201':
          description: OK
components:
  securitySchemes:
        bearerAuth:
            scheme: bearer
            bearerFormat: token
            type: http
security:
  - bearerAuth: []
